  "title": "Registered Nurse #78350",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Healthcare / Medical</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Registered Nurse</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon to Fri 9AM – 6PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $4,500 + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare patients for procedures; verify consent, allergies, and pre-op checks.</li><li>Assist doctors during minor surgeries and procedures; maintain sterile fields.</li><li>Monitor and document patients’ vital signs and recovery; provide post-op instructions.</li><li>Administer medications and perform wound care per protocols.</li><li>Manage instrument reprocessing/sterilization and treatment room turnover.</li><li>Maintain accurate clinical records, inventory, and cold-chain items.</li><li>Uphold infection prevention, medication safety, and emergency readiness.</li><li>Coordinate appointments, patient enquiries, and workflow with the care team.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Nursing</li><li>At least 2 years of nursing experience</li><li>Prior working experience with surgeries is an added advantage</li><li>Registered with Singapore Nursing Board</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78350 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
